{"id":199572,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/12/武汉狠匪炸建行-2死逾10伤-少女爆脑血肉模糊-图慎入/","date":"2011-12-02T17:32:17Z","modified":"2011-12-02T17:32:17Z","title":"武汉狠匪炸建行 2死逾10伤 少女爆脑血肉模糊  (图/慎入)","content":"<p><div>\n</div>\n<p><a name=\"more\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<p><img height=\"432\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-9QYQ5TSgNqQ/TtguNPUIVFI/AAAAAAAABeE/L21QAi4r1Ng/s640/1.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<span><i>歹徒在建行分行引爆放在门口的炸弹，有人当场被炸至重伤，生死未卜。互联网</i></span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span>湖北省武汉市一间建设银行分行门口昨发生爆炸案，传有歹徒引爆放在银行门口的炸弹，由于爆炸威力强大，银行门口被炸出一个大坑，多人被炸至血肉模糊。其中一名 <span>20</span><span>岁妙龄女子，后脑被炸至开花惨死，目前已知爆炸至少造成 </span><span>2</span><span>死逾 </span><span>10</span><span>伤。案件正在调查中。</span></span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span>「准备回家的时候一声巨响整个人都晃了两下，没过一会浓烟四起<span>……</span><span>」案发昨日下午 </span><span>5</span><span>时 </span><span>30</span><span>分，位于武汉关山中学外的建行突然发生爆炸，多名目击网民在微博直击爆炸造成多人伤亡，「现场有六名伤者躺在地上」。</span></span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-mGpT6bnU2mU/TtguQRBaZiI/AAAAAAAABeM/ISUDUjidK1E/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"426\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-mGpT6bnU2mU/TtguQRBaZiI/AAAAAAAABeM/ISUDUjidK1E/s640/2.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<i>有人被炸至血肉模糊，倒卧地上。互联网</i></div>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-NHhNUejAU8Q/TtguULJgsQI/AAAAAAAABeU/l3rWFCgfkmA/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"426\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-NHhNUejAU8Q/TtguULJgsQI/AAAAAAAABeU/l3rWFCgfkmA/s640/3.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<span><i>搜证人员在现场仔细检查瓦砾寻找线索。新华社</i></span></div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span>一名乘的士路经现场的网民称，看见倒地的人中有重伤和死亡，「有死者就在我旁边<span>……</span><span>吓死我了」。一名脑袋被炸开花的女子向一名女网民借电话打给家人求助，「现在我的电话全是血」，直到该名女伤者被救护车送去医院，该网民才安心离开。她心有余悸地说：「幸亏我是坐 </span><span>Taxi</span><span>里面，不然现在重伤或者死的是我吧！」</span></span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span>另一目击者则称，爆炸发出巨响令整个人也站不稳，不久看见爆炸现场冒起浓烟。而关山中学学生也称，爆炸发出巨响，令「所有同学愣住」。</span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-RWrX7RksMh4/TtguYKDvi_I/AAAAAAAABec/LlF9-SCpwic/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"266\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-RWrX7RksMh4/TtguYKDvi_I/AAAAAAAABec/LlF9-SCpwic/s400/4.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<span><i>公安将事发路段封闭，禁止民众接近。互联网</i></span></div>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-uqb6ujz6mhM/Ttguc6cl7LI/AAAAAAAABek/FF-ta1SnMZ4/s1600/5.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"266\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-uqb6ujz6mhM/Ttguc6cl7LI/AAAAAAAABek/FF-ta1SnMZ4/s400/5.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<span>爆炸发生后大批民众围在银行前围观。互联网</span></div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span>内地传媒昨日引述公安消息指，今次爆炸乃特大抢劫案所引发，作案劫匪只有一人！案发时遇劫的建行分行刚好有一辆运钞车到银行运钞，歹徒携炸药抢劫并引爆，但运钞车在爆炸过后仍能行驶，「在现场短暂停留后开走」。目前未知银行损失情况。</span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<img height=\"640\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-IAVHV_iqAOA/TtgupMAtXeI/AAAAAAAABes/eMu165v-WW4/s640/6.jpg\" width=\"425\" />\n</div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span><i>爆炸令银行面目全非，多名公安在现场搜证。新华社</i></span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PwvUUeYSHzk/TtgvOirrVGI/AAAAAAAABe0/_jbDmLNTo2Y/s1600/7.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PwvUUeYSHzk/TtgvOirrVGI/AAAAAAAABe0/_jbDmLNTo2Y/s320/7.jpg\" width=\"213\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span><i>死里逃生的小童一脸惶恐，满身尘土。互联网</i></span></div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span><b>银行门口炸出大坑</b></span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span>武汉公安昨晚在网上公布，爆炸造成 <span>2</span><span>人死亡， </span><span>10</span><span>多人受伤，初步调查，爆炸是由建行旁药店对出堆放的不明物体引发。爆炸将银行门口炸出一个大坑，砖石横飞，其中一名年轻女孩在爆炸中不幸被炸死。公安在案发后封锁现场并展开全面调查，并出动直升机协助调查和追踪。爆炸原因正在调查中。</span></span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span>湖北楚天都市网<span>/</span><span>新浪微博/</span></span><span><span><span>苹果日报</span></span></span></div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/3112334774117141878-6121036255679552966?l=www.molihua.org\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-kn1NvJqqtI5VVW9oBaNSNcnPV4/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-kn1NvJqqtI5VVW9oBaNSNcnPV4/0/di\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-kn1NvJqqtI5VVW9oBaNSNcnPV4/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-kn1NvJqqtI5VVW9oBaNSNcnPV4/1/di\" /></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/molihua/QiRF/~4/Hlt07uID2qQ\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/12/05d0e7011.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":993,"categories":[20534],"tags":[13381]}